# React UI (app code)

- Functional components and hooks only.
- Router: React Router 7; pages in `src/pages/`, shared UI in `src/components/`.
- Global styles: `src/styles/app.css` (prefer extending existing classes over new one-off CSS files).
- Markdown rendering: `MarkdownView`; solution code uses `annotateSolutionCode` + `SolutionCodeTerm`.
- SEO: `PageMeta` + `src/data/seo.ts` for new routes.
- Avoid large bundle growth; no new dependencies unless necessary for the feature.
